channel.title: Runelocus Tool; Status Checker Problem
channel.description: Recently, I had an experienced person teamview me and he fixed all my problems that I had with my server. As he fixed the portforwarding and the firewall exception problem, he went to finish by checking the status of my server. It was still offline. So he recommended me getting a new source, which I did. And it still says that my server is offline. Any suggestions would be very much appreciated.
